      • CYCL_QUERY_SPECIFICATION

        public static final KbCollection CYCL_QUERY_SPECIFICATION
        #$CycLQuerySpecification, the collection of all KBQs. Each instance of CycLQuerySpecification gives a description of how a particular getQueryService should be run by the CycInferenceEngine. At minimum, this description includes the CycL formula that expresses the getQueryService, but can also include a number of other parameters that control inference, such as what microtheory to do the getQueryService in, how much time to allow, etc.
